</li>
<li sourcefile="V1/Installation/Install OSIsoft Adapter for Modbus TCP using Docker.md" sourcestartlinenumber="136" sourceendlinenumber="136"><p sourcefile="V1/Installation/Install OSIsoft Adapter for Modbus TCP using Docker.md" sourcestartlinenumber="136" sourceendlinenumber="136">Name the script <code>modbusdockerstart.sh</code> and save it to the directory where you plan to create the container.</p>
</li>
